Package: boxr
Type: Package
Title: R Interface for the box.com API
Version: 0.0.1
Date: 2015-03-24
Authors@R: person("Brendan", "Rocks", email = "rocks.brendan@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: In addition to uploading and downloading files, boxr includes
  functions which mirror base R operations for local files, (e.g. box_load, 
  box_save, box_read, box_setwd, etc.), as well as 'git style' functions for 
  entire directories (e.g. box_fetch, box_push).
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Imports: 
    httr,
    httpuv,
    assertthat,
    stringr,
    dplyr,
    digest,
    jsonlite
Suggests: testthat
